%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^GREEN%^Plague Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

You wield disease and pestilence like a weapon, bringing whole generations low with your blight.

Clerics with the Plague Domain gain the following benefits:
- Immunity to disease.

The plague domain contains the following spells:

Touch of Sickening, Contagion, Greater Contagion, Epidemic, Plague Storm

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Ebolek

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
